sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant A as Ads Service
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant K as Kafka
    participant M as Moderation Service
    participant I as Indexer
    participant E as Elasticsearch

    U->>G: POST /api/v1/ads
    G->>A: create ad
    A->>P: INSERT ad(status=moderation_pending)
    A->>K: publish ad.created
    A-->>G: 201 Created
    G-->>U: ad_id + moderation_pending

    K->>M: consume ad.created
    M->>K: publish ad.approved
    K->>A: consume ad.approved
    A->>P: UPDATE ad(status=published)
    A->>K: publish ad.published
    K->>I: consume ad.published
    I->>E: index ad document
